text: "Traitor" (stylized in all lowercase) is a song by American singer-songwriter Olivia Rodrigo. It was released to US mainstream radio on August 10, 2021, through Geffen Records. It is the fourth single from Rodrigo's debut album, Sour (2021). It is a indie pop and guitar-rock ballad. ==References== Category:2021 songs Category:Olivia Rodrigo songs
